      public CombustionCar​(OneNightCar.Car.Type type, java.lang.String brand, java.lang.String model, OneNightCar.Car.State state, double GPSLatitude, double GPSLongitude, long odometer, Customer.CustomerLevel customerLevel, float price, double tankSize, double fuelLevel, double consumption, CombustionCar.Transmission transmission, CombustionCar.FuelType fuelType, CarManagementSystem carManagementSystem)
      Creates an ElectricCar with specified ElectricCar Parameters.
      Parameters:
      type - A enum representing the Type of the OneNightCar.Car
      brand - A String representing a OneNightCar.Car Brand
      model - A String representing a OneNightCar.Car Model
      state - A enum representing the State of the OneNightCar.Car (Perfect, Ok, Damaged)
      odometer - A Long representing the odometer Number of the OneNightCar.Car
      GPSLatitude - A double representing the OneNightCar.Car position
      GPSLongitude - A double representing the OneNightCar.Car position
      customerLevel - An enum from Customer representing the User Permission
      price - A float representing the costs of the OneNightCar.Car per Hour
      tankSize - A double representing the max. Tank Size of the OneNightCar.Car
      fuelLevel - A double representing the current Fuel Level
      consumption - A double representing the consumption of the OneNightCar.Car in 100 km
      transmission - An enum representing the Transmission of the OneNightCar.Car (Manuel, Automatic)
      fuelType - an enum representing the Fuel Type of the OneNightCar.Car (Petrol, Diesel)
      carManagementSystem - The system where all the car are saved
